headline: Federal Realty Completes Sale of Levare Apartments at Santana Row
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) today announced the sale of Levare, a 108-unit Class A residential building located within Santana Row in San Jose, California, for $74 million.
